      • terminate

        public void terminate(PublisherSource.Subscriber<?> subscriber,
                      java.lang.Throwable additionalCause)
        Invoke PublisherSource.Subscriber#onError(Throwable) with the passed Throwable if this TerminalNotification is for completion.

        If this TerminalNotification is for error, then the passed Throwable will be added as a suppressed cause to the existing Throwable. If this is an error notification, the associated cause will get updated with the additionalCause.

        Parameters:
        subscriber - to terminate.
        additionalCause - Throwable which is used as the caus
